window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Step into a captivating world, hundreds of years in the future, where the past has left a haunting legacy and elemental energy pulses through the veins of a chosen few.. .</p> <p>In this dystopian realm, those once known as witches are now hailed as kinterra, guardians of the delicate harmony between humanity and the natural world.</p> <p>Meet Zoi, a headstrong and spirited young woman. As she approaches her fifteenth birthday, her life takes a fateful turn when she is chosen to embrace her kinterra heritage. Zoi is reluctant to accept her magical lineage, dismissing it as mere fantasy.</p> <p>But Zoi's belief in magic ignites as she trains with her aunt, a powerful kinterra. She meets Basil, a fellow apprentice with a burning desire to find his long-lost sister, kidnapped years before. Amidst their shared pursuit of mastery over the elements, an undeniable spark ignites between them, kindling a romance that flickers amidst the shadows of their challenging quest.</p> <p>As Zoi's training progresses, the unexpected abduction of her mentor ignites fear and doubt in Zoi’s heart. Together with Basil, she embarks on a perilous rescue mission, using their elemental prowess to track down their teacher and liberate her.</p> <p>As more kinterra go missing, Zoi, Basil, and their friends set out on a journey to find them. A sinister plot unravels, revealing a despicable man driven by a twisted thirst for magic. With the fate of kinterra hanging in the balance, the ultimate battle awaits.</p> <p>The spellbinding tale of <b>Order of Terra</b> takes listeners on a thrilling and magical journey through a world where elemental energy and the human spirit converge. Can Zoi and her companions save their kind from the clutches of darkness? Find out in this enthralling dystopian fantasy, where the power of the elements and the heart's longing intertwine in a wondrous tapestry of courage and love.</p>"; 
